        <section class="faq-section">
            <div class="section-header">
                <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-container">
                <div class="faq-item" id="faq1">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq('faq1')">
                        How do I register for online voting?
                        <i class="icon-right" data-feather="chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>First-time voters must register at any designated enrollment center with valid ID and proof
                            of citizenship. Once registered, you'll receive a Bharatque voter ID that can be activated for
                            online voting through our secure portal.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" id="faq2">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq('faq2')">
                        Is online voting secure?
                        <i class="icon-right" data-feather="chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Our platform uses military-grade encryption, blockchain technology, multi-factor
                            authentication, and end-to-end verifiability to ensure your vote remains secure, anonymous,
                            and tamper-proof throughout the election process.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" id="faq3">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq('faq3')">
                        What if I experience technical issues during voting?
                        <i class="icon-right" data-feather="chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Contact our support team immediately at support@evoteindia.in or call our help desk. We
                            maintain 24/7 technical support during election periods and can assist with
                            re-authentication or issue resolution without compromising your ballot secrecy.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item" id="faq4">
                    <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq('faq4')">
                        Can non-resident Indians (NRIs) vote in elections?
                        <i class="icon-right" data-feather="chevron-down"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Registered NRIs can participate in national elections through our platform. You must have a
                            valid Indian passport and enrollment in the NRI voter registry. State elections eligibility
                            varies - check our voter guidelines section for constituency-specific regulations.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
